{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6129","heading":"Certification of completion of milestones with respect to plutonium pit aging","label":"6129 Certification of completion of milestones with respect to plutonium pit aging","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptVI/sptB/ch602/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe date of the enactment of this Act, referred to in subsecs. (b)(1) and (c), is the date of enactment of , which was approved .Pub. L. 119–60Dec. 18, 2025","Prior ProvisionsProvisions similar to those in this section were contained in , which was set out as a note under , War and National Defense, prior to repeal by .section 3124 of Pub. L. 117–263section 2538a of Title 50Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(b)(11)"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Requirement","label":"a .—Requirement","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Administrator shall complete the milestones on plutonium pit aging identified in the report entitled “Research Program Plan for Plutonium and Pit Aging”, published by the Administration in September 2021.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Assessments","label":"b .—Assessments","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"acting through the Defense Programs Advisory Committee, conduct biennial reviews during the period beginning not later than one year after the date of the enactment of this Act and ending , regarding the progress achieved toward completing the milestones described in subsection (a); andDecember 31, 2030","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"seek to enter into an arrangement with the private scientific advisory group known as JASON to conduct, not later than 2030, an assessment of plutonium pit aging.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Briefings","label":"c .—Briefings","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the progress achieved toward completing the milestones described in subsection (a); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the results of the assessments described in subsection (b).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":".—Certification of Completion of Milestones","label":"d .—Certification of Completion of Milestones","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"certify to the congressional defense committees whether the milestones described in subsection (a) have been achieved; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"describing the reasons such milestones have not been achieved;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"including, if the Administrator determines the Administration will not be able to meet one of such milestones, an explanation for that determination; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6129/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6129%2Fd%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"specifying new dates for the completion of the milestones the Administrator anticipates the Administration will meet.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
